overview:
I Web Services is a young, dynamic web design & development company having development office in Noida - India & an International Sales Office in Canada. In a vision to transform designs to fully functional website at an affordable price, I Web Services provide quality service at an affordable price. With experience and energetic XHTML and Open Source Developers we make sure your website is delivered in time, within budget and up to the standard that we promise.

In our service offerings we offer a range of value-for-money solutions including Website Design, Web Development, Content Management Systems (CMS) and Mobile Application Development on Android and iOS based devices. Our dynamic application development platform uses a state-of-the-art framework that comprises high performance AJAX libraries including jQuery, Prototype, script.aculo.us, YUI Library, Mootools, PHP 5, MySQL on Amazon EC2.

So, if you have been searching for I Web Services to help you build your dream website with the best open source technology stack then send a message and we will be happy to help you.
